        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-emerald-500 z-0"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 border-b-4 border-r-4 border-emerald-500 z-0"></div>
        <div
          class="relative z-10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
        >
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160550-2173dba999ef?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200"
            alt="Conference Mission"
            class="w-full h-[500px] object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-emerald-900/10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="text-emerald-600 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-6">Conference Overview</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#062C1B] leading-tight mb-8">
          Bridging Innovation and Human Care
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            We are pleased to invite you to the Healthcare Excellence and Advancements in Life Treatment & Human
            Medicine – International Conference (HEALTHMED-IC), a global forum dedicated to strengthening clinical
            excellence, accelerating medical and technological innovation, and advancing human-centered healthcare.
          </p>
          <p>
            HEALTHMED-IC brings together researchers, clinicians, biomedical engineers, pharmacists, nurses, public
            health professionals, policymakers, and industry innovators to exchange knowledge and develop actionable
            solutions to today’s most pressing health challenges. Through interdisciplinary dialogue, the conference
            aims to bridge scientific discovery with real-world practice, supporting safer care, better outcomes, and
            more resilient health systems.
          </p>
          <p>
            With the theme “Bridging Technology and Humanity: Advancing Global Health Excellence through Innovation and
            Sustainable Medicine”, HEALTHMED-IC highlights the critical intersection of: Medical and clinical sciences,
            Biomedical engineering and medical technologies, Health informatics and AI in medicine, Pharmaceutical
            sciences and clinical pharmacy, Public health, epidemiology, and environmental health, Nursing, midwifery,
            allied health, and mental health.
          </p>
          <p>
            We warmly invite you to participate by submitting your abstracts and full papers, presenting your research,
            and engaging in high-impact discussions. HEALTHMED-IC welcomes both onsite and virtual participation,
            ensuring an inclusive and globally connected academic and professional experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            Together, let us shape the future of healthcare, where innovation advances responsibly, systems become more
            sustainable, and medicine remains grounded in humanity. We look forward to welcoming you to HEALTHMED-IC.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
